Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/faadzlan/dotvim.git $HOME/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s $HOME/.vim/vimrc $HOME/.vimrc
    ln -s $HOME/.vim/bashrc $HOME/.bashrc
    ln -s $HOME/.vim/gvimrc $HOME/.gvimrc
    ln -s $HOME/.vim/vifmrc $HOME/.config/vifm/vifmrc

Switch to the `$HOME/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd $HOME/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
